.............................................</p>\r\n\r\n<p>....................................................................................................................................................................</p>\r\n\r\n<p>....................................................................................................................................................................</p>\r\n\r\n<p>....................................................................................................................................................................</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>JUKNIS VERIFIKATOR DALAM SELEKSI ADMINISTRASI :</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Scan ASLI e-KTP (berwarna)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Scan ASLI Surat Lamaran</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Scan ASLI Ijazah (berwarna)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Scan Transkrip Nilai (berwarna)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Pas Photo terbaru dengan menggunakan kemeja putih dengan latar belakang merah</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. Scan ASLI Surat Pernyataan Data Diri Pelamar (berwarna)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. Surat Keterangan bernomor, bertanggal, ditandatangani Dokter Rumah Sakit Pemerintah/Puskesmas, distempel.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>....................................................................................................................................................................</p>\r\n\r\n<p>....................................................................................................................................................................</p>\r\n\r\n<p>....................................................................................................................................................................</p>\r\n\r\n<p>....................................................................................................................................................................</p>\r\n\r\n<p>..................................................................................................................